{
  "stem": "1413.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when my father was out of work sometimes, and the kosher meat and the kosher stuff was a little higher than the regular, she couldn't afford.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not that she did eat chozzer-- far from it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She ate then-- she had meat and butter and whatever from a Jewish store.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But not kosher, but not treif, either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, he stayed in bed and home for most of the day but Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't go to shul.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He fasted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So did my mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The light just dimmed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't-- and we had to-- when it was the day of Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The day of Yom Kippur, then we ate late at night, as you all know that it is customary to eat, I think it was herring at the time, and cheese and special kind of bread, and all that kind-- I don't have to-- that's the way that life was with the family.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had uncles and aunts and nephews and cousins, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but if you ask me-- if you're going to ask me, I volunteer it to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't-- I'm almost 90%-- 100% sure that none of my aunts, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] maybe one of two cousins, came back-- who I spoke and now I remember.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But from a family, my closest family was 18 people, children and in-laws.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Only one of my family came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that is the youngest child of my youngest-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] who is still alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was named after my uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that didn't a week go by or my mother made me go to visit him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, my father's sister was never married.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
